io.boodskap.iot.plugin

Annotation Type Plugin


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface Plugin

    Every plugin must have this annotation declared

    Author:
    Jegan Vincent

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      String id
      A unique identifier for this plugin, typically a UUID in string format
      PluginType type
      Type of the plugin
      String version
      Plugin version, semver style versioning is strongly recommended

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      String contextId
      If the plugin is a type of PluginType.CONTEXT then a unique context-id is required
